column3: it was my final semester and i was really stressed out.  then
column4: my personal almost-relationship thing. i took 4 years to heal the wound that my ex left
column5: and i fell for this guy who i will named A. it was magical
column6: magically painful. it’s been four years that no one can affect my mood and i am always a carefree lady. i fell hard
column7: and that’s when he walked out on me. i pretended nothing has happened because i told myself i am strong. but clearly i’m not.  and for anyone who can’t reach me recently
column8: I’ll come back to you soon
column10: i deleted my kkt because it deletes msg when i did not open it for days
column11: so reach me here alright?  anyone who is reading this
column12: be strong and love yourself more than anyone would
